{"tid":1527860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊擊戰出路 全民組隊","createTime":"2019-09-01T11:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T07:38:34.000Z","uid":167938,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12123b8e4310604aa4b8ce6996361263ade9233f","tid":1527860,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"平民服裝<br />\n同7個朋友 組成8人小隊<br />\n令人持有兩支大裝藍妹<br />\n每日 清晨6點半 下午4點半<br />\n到自己個區狗屋 掉入去 即走<br />\n直至狗總守備力量太強 再轉下一個政府機關<br />\n要讓所有返政府工既人恐懼 驚到工都唔敢返<br />\n直至解散政府呢個邪惡體制<br />\n<br />\n唔可以用白電油 炭含量太低 <br />\n要用車用電油 鬼油<br />\n鄉下地方係最多武器 廢車拆後座泵油 <br />\n成本只係架車有漸味 而家渣幾公里就散到<br />\n<br />\n明刀明槍只做和平集會<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong on fire<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死線係美國落實制裁香港法案<br />\n美國制裁後 香港人並不會立即贏<br />\n而係比中共拖垮  香港人依然不會立即有民主<br />\n<br />\n遊擊戰要抗爭到 <br />\n局勢升級到中共鎮壓<br />\n太子站明顯就係中共鎮壓<br />\n國際開戰制裁中共為止<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong people don&rsquo;t only be water<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">be fire 🔥 </span></span>"},{"pid":"6dee9c4e6f6e18a6a89877b98f4b37529f14ead6","tid":1527860,"uid":167938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:44:50.000Z","msg":"我正式和警賊宣戰"},{"pid":"369f640b4012d2a9acf22caed9f417ca02f0eb44","tid":1527860,"uid":293227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"此po 必推"},{"pid":"825e3a4c985e31638fdc3884e8d778eb7b14f027","tid":1527860,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Hong Kong on fire!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"b0459f7db5818a666ef48d0d0ec9c79d1c6d6bae","tid":1527860,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c1e8be76461dd2ba648404c1b178c05c4713c4","tid":1527860,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"政治不是